✨HUGE GIVEAWAY ALERT✨
On 10th June, Style Fashion Etc is completing 12 years!!! To celebrate this momentous occasion, we are hosting a HUGE Giveaway with not 1, not 2, not 3 but 🌟12 WINNERS🌟!!!
Honestly, I am so grateful for my absolutely amazing audience that I personally want to hug and say a heartfelt thank you to each and everyone of you gorgeous people❤️ 

Here are few easy peasy things you can do to participate in the giveaway:
1. Follow @SrishtiSBhatia (Yes, @stylefashionetc is now @srishtisbhatia)
2. Leave a comment about your experience or how you feel about me and my content (I want to know your genuine emotions and feedback for me!). 

Few extra things you can do only if you want to:
1. Engage with my content! Your every single like, comment, save and share can do wonders for my content that I work hard to create every day. And trust me, I know my regular audience and they would be getting brownie points😉
2. Tag your friends, share the giveaway, invite people to participate! The more the merrier!  This would earn you extra entries and make your chances of winning much higher. 

Also, few more things you should know about this giveaway:
1. The products you see in this video is only half of the total products! We could not fit everything in the shoot so decided to shoot half only😅
2. Apart from the beauty goodies, you will be getting handmade cookies by yours truly❤️
3. The Giveway will run for 20 days and the winners will be announced LIVE on 10th June! 

Best of luck to you all and a huge thank you for making my dreams come true! Without you all, I won’t be where I am and I won’t be having my dream career❤️✨
